rComments: I'm doing this as a favor to all students at the University of Toronto.  I attend Albion College in Michigan, the institution Dr. Hagerman taught at before.  You simply must take any history course he offers.  Grades ridiculously rough on papers, but proper proofreading does the trick.  He's the best professor I've ever had.  10/10 would recommend.
A pretty good TA. Harsh grader.
Helpful and very knowledgeable.  Knows his stuff.  Fun to discuss issues with...unless you don't do your work!
